<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Small Crafted Gauntlets Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Purchase 2 Star Rubies.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to South Karana and kill Avocets to retrieve an Aviak Charm.<BR>
<BR>
3) Head to the Centaur City in South Karana and hail Shakrn to receive the quest.<BR>
<BR>
4) Give the Aviak Charm and the 2 Star Rubies to Shakrn to receive the Crafted Gauntlets.<BR>
<BR>
5) Take the Crafted Gauntlets to West Commons and find the two dwarves near the toll booth, who are in full plate.  Hail them both, and ask "What do you resize?" to find out which one resizes the Crafted Gauntlets.  Simply give the proper dwarf the gauntlets, and you will receive Small Crafted Gaunlets in return, which are exactly the same, but with reduced weight.</div>
<BR>
